vote.title: Authorize a three-year cooperative purchasing agreement for citywide fire alarm inspection services with Protegis, LLC dba ISA Fire & Security through an Interlocal Agreement with Dallas County - Estimated amount of $250,000 - Financing: General Fund ($127,550), Dallas Water Utilities Fund ($67,650), and Aviation Fund ($54,800)
